Class VLCJIntegratedPlayer

  • java.lang.Object

      • com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.frame.map.MapIntegratedPlayer

  • public class VLCJIntegratedPlayer
extends VideoPlayerBase
    A VLCJ integrated player used to play videos in Minecraft. The library uses a callback for the specific function from native libraries.
